summary:
- **FY25 Revenue Guidance**: $212M–$216M (down from $294M in FY24) due to:  
  - Suspension at Grosvenor mine (June 2024),  
  - Closure of Integra mine (Aug 2024),  
  - Reduced activity at Moranbah North mine (Q4 FY25).  

- **FY25 Underlying EBITDA Guidance**: $11.0M–$13.0M (vs. $27.5M in FY24 ex-one-offs).  
- **Adjustments**: $1.4M inventory provisions, $0.7M asset impairment.  
- **Net Cash Position (30 Jun 2025)**: $29.0M (up from $21.8M in FY24).  
- **Next Update**: Full results on 27 Aug 2025.
